data.description: Welcome to your new home! This spacious home includes 2 bedrooms and 3 bonus rooms that could easily be used as additional bedrooms, or whatever your heart desires! The oversized kitchen has plenty of space for all of your cooking needs and space for a dining area. Spend less time on yard work and more time doing what you love with the low maintenance back yard! With just under 1300 square feet, 2-5 bedrooms, one large bathroom, a fully fenced back yard, and more, this is the one you've been waiting for!
